reviewText: My son Super Why so we got him this and he loves it.

Good DVD Good Price  I would recommend this to any one that has small children.  It was a gift for my nephew
Kids love super why and was great for a long car trip .  Kept them entertain the whole way there.

I love the way they show the children what happen when they change a word.  How this can change the whole line of the story.  They also spell the words out.  This all come from one of the children having a problem.
A fun way for kids to learn about reading and healthy eating.
My girls love this show and i like that it is educational.
My kids 2 & 3, both love Super Why.  I especially liked the focus on health:)  Talking about fruits/veggies and that candy/soda aren't good to keep your body fueled.  Cute!
My nephew loved it! I enjoy how super why creators take time & let kids learn with a good moral to story.
